data.description: Charming Doublewide Mobile Home on 9.02 Acres - Horses Allowed Welcome to your own slice of country paradise just minutes from Rapid City and Box Elder. This spacious doublewide mobile home offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and rural tranquility. Situated on a generous 9.02-acre lot, this property is a horse lover's dream come true. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity!  Property Highlights:  • Total Living Space: 1800 sq ft on the main level • Additional 1800 sq ft of unfinished basement for future expansion • 3 Bedrooms, perfect for a family or guests • 2 Bathrooms, including a master suite with ensuite bathroom • Spacious living area for family gatherings • Bright and open kitchen with ample cabinet space • Cozy dining area with a view of the picturesque surroundings • Attached 34 ft x 56 ft garage for all your storage and parking needs and a horse barn!!
